- src/ui/tui.rs: borders_enabled state, hotkey, render logic
- src/ui/tui.rs: TuiStatePersisted struct, save/load

**Testing**:
- F11 toggles borders on/off
- Borders persist across sessions
- Layout adjusts correctly with borders
